highlights.text: Saibo by Sachin-Jigar, Shreya Ghoshal, and Tochi Raina is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Imphal, up 28 spots at #65.
Maan Meri Jaan by King has been on Top Songs Imphal the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Imphal. Reminder is the highest at #1.
Shape of You by Ed Sheeran is the highest new entry on Top Songs Imphal at #99.
